margin值将内容放置到border模拟的栏上去*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">float</span>:left;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"表格边框单线显示\"><a href=\"#表格边框单线显示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"表格边框单线显示\"></a>表格边框单线显示</h1><p>表格单元格的边框默认是双线边框，显示为单一的边框：</p>\n<p>在<code>table</code>上应用<code>border-collapse:collapse;</code>即可。</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"css","path":"api/categories/css.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"border","path":"api/tags/border.json"}]}